title: Gorgeous 2 bed/ 2 bath Townhouse in West Bloomington
posting_body: ['Welcome Home!', 'I am looking to rent a nice Townhouse in West Bloomington.', 'Awesome neighborhood near Old Shakopee Rd/Bush Lake Rd in West Bloomington.', 'This is a great townhouse (end unit).', 'This is a 2 bedroom , 2 bath unit that has over 1400 square feet.', 'This unit is available September 1, 2022 and possibly earlier if interested!', 'This is a great townhouse with high end finishes.', ' The main level has a living room, kitchen and bathroom.', 'There is also a patio off the main level.', ' High end appliances, counter tops and a great gas fire place.', 'The upstairs has 2 bedrooms and a loft.', ' There is also a bathroom upstairs.', 'There is a 2 car attached garage with entry into the house from the garage.', '- easy access to I494/I35W/Hwy 100/Hwy 169', '- Bloomington schools (Jefferson high school)', '-I am asking $1820 per month rent', '-Unlawful detainer will disqualify you', '-Background check will be completed including criminal history and credit history.', '-$2,000 security deposit due at time of lease agreement.', '-First month rent due on move in date', '-Pets OK with additional monthly fee and additional security deposit', '- Must follow association rules', '- I DO NOT accept section 8...sorry!', 'I am a license Realtor and owner of the house.', ' If you decide to rent this unit with hopes of buying a house, this is a great opportunity.', ' If you hire me help with the new home purchase I will let you out of the lease with no fees or penalty when your new purchase closes.', ' Great Flexibility!!!!!!']
